@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title Volume Group Snapshots - Crash-Consistent (K8s 1.32)

package "Application Database Distribuée" as app {
  database "PVC Data\n/var/lib/db/data" as pvc1 #90EE90
  database "PVC Logs\n/var/lib/db/logs" as pvc2 #90EE90
  database "PVC WAL\n/var/lib/db/wal" as pvc3 #90EE90

  rectangle "Pod Database" as pod #87CEEB
  pod -down-> pvc1
  pod -down-> pvc2
  pod -down-> pvc3
}

package "Sans Group Snapshot" as without #FFB6C1 {
  rectangle "Snapshot 1\nt=0.00s" as s1
  rectangle "Snapshot 2\nt=0.05s" as s2
  rectangle "Snapshot 3\nt=0.10s" as s3

  note bottom
    ❌ **Inconsistant!**
    Les snapshots sont pris
    à des moments différents
    → Corruption possible
  end note
}

package "Avec Group Snapshot" as with #90EE90 {
  rectangle "VolumeGroupSnapshot" as vgs #FFD700 {
    rectangle "Snap Data\nt=0.00s" as gs1
    rectangle "Snap Logs\nt=0.00s" as gs2
    rectangle "Snap WAL\nt=0.00s" as gs3
  }

  note bottom
    ✅ **Crash-Consistent!**
    Tous les snapshots pris
    au même instant
    → Intégrité garantie
  end note
}

pvc1 -down-> s1 : séquentiel
pvc2 -down-> s2
pvc3 -down-> s3

pvc1 -down-> gs1 : atomique
pvc2 -down-> gs2
pvc3 -down-> gs3

note bottom
  **Configuration:**
  ```yaml
  apiVersion: groupsnapshot.storage.k8s.io/v1alpha1
  kind: VolumeGroupSnapshot
  metadata:
    name: db-backup-2024
  spec:
    volumeGroupSnapshotClassName: csi-snapclass
    source:
      selector:
        matchLabels:
          app: database
  ```
end note

legend right
  |= Cas d'usage |= Besoin |
  | PostgreSQL | Data + WAL |
  | MongoDB | Data + Journal |
  | Cassandra | Data + Commitlog |
  | Elasticsearch | Indices multiples |
endlegend

@enduml
